<del rend="strikethrough">Rewplich </del> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> hat </del> vnd gerawbt hat / von <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_353_r1l11">wilhelm Groſſen gekaufft <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / das niht cʒimlich ıſt </ab><ab facs="#facs_353_r1l13"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ~ 
